---

<section id="contacto" class="relative text-center overflow-hidden pt-24 px-6">
  <div class="cta-blob" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <span class="reveal block text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-accent mb-5 relative z-10">Trabajemos juntos</span>

  <h2 class="reveal font-bold uppercase text-white relative z-10" style="--stagger:1; font-size:clamp(3rem,8vw,80px); line-height:0.95; letter-spacing:1.28px; max-width:900px; margin:0 auto;">
    <span class="block">Empecemos</span>
    <span class="block">a construir</span>
  </h2>

  <p class="reveal relative z-10 text-[16px] font-light leading-[1.7] text-white/50 max-w-[400px] mx-auto mt-5 mb-10" style="--stagger:2;">
    Contanos en qué está tu negocio y encontramos juntos la mejor solución tecnológica.
  </p>

  <div class="reveal relative z-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4" style="--stagger:3;">
    <a href="mailto:hola@chcstudio.cr" class="filled-button">
      Escribinos ahora
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M4 12 L12 4 M5.5 4 H12 V10.5"></path>
      </svg>
    </a>
    <a href="#proyectos" class="ghost-button" style="border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.30); color:rgba(255,255,255,0.60);">Ver proyectos</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-blob {
    position: absolute;
    width: 600px; height: 300px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, #01c38e 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0.06;
    filter: blur(80px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
</style>
